If I skipped every investment because of past mishaps I would close off my investments to only slow, lethargic, and well managed blue chips like Kraft, which as it seems, also make mistakes. I think the future holds an extreme appetite for all sorts of energy, and fossil fuels are limited, so I think if ASTI can move from a smallcap with lots of problems to a smallcap that executes well, they will read the handsome rewards..
NOt 30min into the game the blue screen came back. Now it seems to me that it was the game causing this. i reinstalled the game let my computer chill for a day when back to play and everything was fin for like 3days. I want to update the firmware in the hope that doing so will aid me in configuring the MFP to work with Office 365 (a cloud based software as a service solution). Cutting a long story short the Ricoh in it's current form simply cannot be configured for Office 365. No support technician is asking me to do this.
Since each segment is only about twelve and a half minutes long, Exposition Guy is used as a running gag to further the plot quickly and easily, often adding comedy as a bonus (Something that WordGirl once pointed out by saying "Sometimes we need helpgetting to the next scene").
